						               													<description>Play your cards and bake the best pizzas in town!&amp;#10;Points are earned by baking pizzas with ingredients from your hand. Who will be the best baker, who will bake the Super Pizza?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Several pizza cards are open, depending on number of players. Small pizzas worth 5 points, medium worth 10 and large worth 20 points.&amp;#10;Each player holds 5 cards, drawing another at the start of their turn, which could either be ingredients to bake a pizza (collect it if you have the required ingredients) or event cards that must be played to remove them from a player's hand to make room for ingredients.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A player may also discard 3 ingredients to open an event card. After an event a player cannot fill up their hand or play event cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If there are no more pizza cards of a single size left, 5 ingredients will be flipped over to create the super pizza.&amp;#10;Once only one pizza type cards are left, or the super pizza has been baked, the game ends, and players count points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
